fields.description:
{html}<div><p>Right now you can only add one button to each of leftNavButton
and rightNavButton, this is ok for iPhone, but for iPad there
should be possible to add multiple buttons to the navbar.</p></div>{html}

comments.body:
{html}<div><p>Use a button bar</p>
<pre>
<code>var bb1 = Titanium.UI.createButtonBar({
    labels:['+', '-'],
    backgroundColor:'#336699',
    style:Titanium.UI.iPhone.SystemButtonStyle.BAR,
});

win.rightNavButton = bb1;</code>
</pre></div>{html}
